Package org.gridgain.client

Public API for GridGain Java client.

See:
          Description

Interface Summary
GridClient Java client API.
GridClientCompute A compute projection of grid client.
GridClientConfiguration Java client configuration.
GridClientData A data projection of grid client.
GridClientDataAffinity Interface that will determine which node should be connected by the client when operation on a key is requested.
GridClientDataConfiguration Java client data projection configuration.
GridClientFuture<R> Future for asynchronous operations.
GridClientNode Node descriptor.
GridClientPredicate<E1> Defines predicate construct.
GridClientTopologyListener Listener interface for notifying on nodes joining or leaving remote grid.
 

Class Summary
GridArgumentCheck This class encapsulates argument check (null and range) for public facing APIs.
GridClientConfigurationAdapter Client configuration adapter.
GridClientDataConfigurationAdapter Data configuration bean.
GridClientFactory Client factory opens and closes clients.
GridClientPartitionedAffinity Affinity function for partitioned cache.
 

Enum Summary
GridClientCacheMode Cache type on remote node.
GridClientProtocol Protocol that will be used when client connections are created.
 

Exception Summary
GridClientAuthenticationException Exception that represents client authentication failure for some reason.
GridClientClosedException This exception is thrown whenever a closed client is attempted to be used.
GridClientException Client exception.
GridServerUnreachableException This exception is thrown when none of the servers specified in client configuration can be connected to within timeout.
